# Anchorpipe A11y Rules (WCAG 2.2)

- Baseline AA; target AAA on Global Overview, Test Detail, PR surfaces.
- Structure: semantic landmarks (<main>, <nav>, headings), correct ARIA only when necessary.
- Keyboard: full access, logical tab order, visible focus, skip links, no traps.
- Color/contrast: >= 4.5:1 text; provide high-contrast theme.
- Motion: respect prefers-reduced-motion.
- Forms: associated labels, aria-live for inline errors, clear helper text/examples.
- Testing: run axe on polished pages; add manual SR and keyboard passes; block merge on critical violations.
